title: Episode 60 w/ Swizz Beatz (Part 2)
itunes:title: Episode 60 w/ Swizz Beatz (Part 2)
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with super producer Swizz Beatz. In this two part episode the guys talk about DMX, Ruff Ryers, art, his involvement with Bacardi, how his career got started and a lot more! --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
